{"tid":404152,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇比較好既兔醫生介紹？跪求","createTime":"2017-09-17T21:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T03:08:33.000Z","uid":22349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"41edd538e6e89009310e2ce911646f46797dd74b","tid":404152,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T21:09:44.000Z","msg":"帶隻兔睇過大圍Dr. Lim, 大角咀Dr. Ma, 好似情況都係咁上下，佢食左個幾月藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到都心痛<br />\n想幫佢轉個醫生，唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇話咩補健品岩佢食，增兔抵抗力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/050929_7b3805232b849cdf0e8fc2953b66535f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F050929_7b3805232b849cdf0e8fc2953b66535f.jpg&h=c87c6d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/050942_538660e4fcf33812cc08684ef2a55eb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F050942_538660e4fcf33812cc08684ef2a55eb2.jpg&h=c064012d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e3b3372c9e2b66197fb88be072e044ba10ac303","tid":404152,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T21:12:46.000Z","msg":"佢打乞嗤，流透明鼻水，但食食吓藥直情變咗白色鼻涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好極都好唔到，睇左3次醫生"},{"pid":"c27fb3fc03e692af418aa105ec66cf49ed59b856","tid":404152,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep